        "subject": "LU-17361 tests: change $TGT to local disk dir in lustre-rsync-test",
        "message": "LU-17361 tests: change $TGT to local disk dir in lustre-rsync-test\n\nThis patch changes the lustre_rsync target filesystem from\ntmpfs $TMP to a local disk dir to see if this can resolve\nthe timeout failure.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial env=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes \\\n  testlist=lustre-rsync-test,lustre-rsync-test,lustre-rsync-test\n\nChange-Id: I0c344e5f8e64ea84e1a84367eb25c86a51a57efe\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/61637\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Frederick Dilger <fdilger@whamcloud.com>\n"
